06:08.362 --> 06:10.202
Oh, you don't need to
do anything with me.

06:11.223 --> 06:14.516
Yeah, maybe I'm too naive and
reckless for you to be bothered with.

06:35.586 --> 06:36.685
Where have you been?

06:37.331 --> 06:38.549
Doctor's appointment.

06:40.226 --> 06:42.101
So, Wilson had me write a bench memo

06:42.126 --> 06:44.688
arguing against allowing the
personnel records in as evidence.

06:45.162 --> 06:47.656
I knocked it out of the park,
if I do say so myself.

06:47.681 --> 06:49.933
- He let you read them?
- No.

06:50.976 --> 06:52.567
Don't you think that's unusual?

06:52.982 --> 06:55.550
To ask you to defend a position
on a document you haven't read?

06:56.278 --> 06:57.518
I really don't care.

06:59.069 --> 07:00.660
Do you care about anything, Ben?

07:00.755 --> 07:02.555
Except for career advancement?

07:07.688 --> 07:09.363
You know, my father
took a job as a janitor

07:09.387 --> 07:11.638
in one of the best college
prep-schools in the country,

07:11.952 --> 07:14.432
so he could get a discount on
the tuition for me to go there.

07:16.147 --> 07:18.507
My mother worked seven
days a week waiting tables.

07:19.889 --> 07:21.409
If I get to be a Supreme Court clerk,

07:21.434 --> 07:24.178
I'll get a 300K signing bonus
at any law firm of my choosing.

07:25.363 --> 07:27.732
I'm going to use that money to
buy my parents a house. So...

07:28.849 --> 07:30.567
career advancement, sure.

07:31.480 --> 07:33.528
But what motivates me most, is
taking care of the two people

07:33.552 --> 07:35.192
who made all this possible for me.

07:38.589 --> 07:39.661
You know, Callie,

07:40.029 --> 07:41.811
you could have gone straight
to work at a non-profit,

07:41.835 --> 07:42.935
but don't kid yourself.

07:43.396 --> 07:45.836
You applied for this clerkship
for the same reason we all did.

07:47.223 --> 07:49.276
It's an elite path to success,
and you know it.

07:49.732 --> 07:50.849
Good night.

08:08.812 --> 08:09.870
Yes?

08:12.535 --> 08:14.161
I'd like to offer precedent

08:14.186 --> 08:16.977
that would allow you to
let the personnel files in.

08:17.346 --> 08:20.193
I think that these records
are extremely relevant

08:20.218 --> 08:21.704
to the plaintiff's Monell claim

08:21.729 --> 08:23.561
that the city had an informal policy

08:23.586 --> 08:25.633
to let suspects die instead
of giving them critical care.

08:25.657 --> 08:27.282
How do you know what's inside the files?

08:27.551 --> 08:30.059
The Supreme Court held
in Connick v. Thompson

08:30.083 --> 08:31.918
that plaintiffs could prove
deliberate indifference...

08:31.942 --> 08:33.142
You didn't answer my question.

08:34.087 --> 08:37.378
Did you... take the
files from this office?

08:38.706 --> 08:39.756
No, sir.

08:39.883 --> 08:41.543
They were sent to me anonymously.

08:41.568 --> 08:43.607
Why would someone send you the files?

08:45.789 --> 08:46.789
I don't know why.

08:47.686 --> 08:49.769
But I didn't show them to anyone.

08:49.794 --> 08:52.364
- I give you my word on that.
- The Monell claim doesn't apply.

08:52.730 --> 08:55.506
There's no evidence that this
was an actual police policy.

08:55.531 --> 08:58.274
- It's a comment made by one man.
- The police chief.

08:58.454 --> 09:00.617
This is smoking-gun evidence of notice

09:00.642 --> 09:02.151
by the policymaker himself.

09:02.176 --> 09:03.284
You're stretching the precedent

09:03.308 --> 09:06.480
to provide the outcome you want,
not the law supporting it.

09:08.788 --> 09:10.371
With all due respect, Your Honor,

09:10.717 --> 09:12.458
you may think you're
not an activist judge,

09:12.483 --> 09:15.987
but you have consistently protected
the police as an institution

09:16.012 --> 09:18.813
regardless of the actions
of individual officers.

09:19.415 --> 09:21.595
There is no such thing
as an impartial judge

09:21.620 --> 09:23.066
on the left or the right.

09:23.091 --> 09:24.593
You choose conservative precedents,

09:24.618 --> 09:27.018
not because you have to,
because you want to.

09:29.069 --> 09:30.160
Is that all?

09:31.236 --> 09:32.276
Yes, sir.

09:33.216 --> 09:36.034
