11:11.660 --> 11:15.706
It's just, you know, sometimes the
first time with someone can be...

11:16.124 --> 11:18.175
not as good as the second time.

11:19.010 --> 11:21.457
The second time was just as
amazing as the first time.

11:22.652 --> 11:24.268
Wait till the third time.

11:24.587 --> 11:26.637
That's when I really
pull out all the tricks.

11:26.662 --> 11:28.345
Oh, he has tricks.

11:29.111 --> 11:32.172
Come on, the Kamasutra came from India.

11:32.197 --> 11:34.714
Ooh, maybe we should
make a Kamasutra app.

11:35.808 --> 11:38.126
