11:45.550 --> 11:47.988
She quit because she got a
better offer somewhere else.

11:48.532 --> 11:50.475
It's not him I need to worry about,

11:50.500 --> 11:53.960
it's the sexist nerds that work for him.

11:54.266 --> 11:56.366
