14:11.985 --> 14:13.461
Yes. Yes, we do.

14:13.486 --> 14:15.878
- From, uh, Davia's birthday.
- Right. Yeah.

14:15.974 --> 14:19.149
- How you doing?
- Great. Good.

14:19.174 --> 14:20.556
I'm sorry, I was just, uh...

14:20.581 --> 14:23.274
Oh, it's fine. I actually
have to go anyway.

14:23.299 --> 14:25.049
So, um, I'll text you later.

14:25.758 --> 14:26.833
Great.

14:28.737 --> 14:30.630
