14:30.655 --> 14:33.556
- No worries.
- Uh, is Callie around?

14:33.781 --> 14:36.517
Uh, if she's not in the lounge,
I would try the roof?

14:36.816 --> 14:37.816
Will do.

14:38.525 --> 14:40.851
- It's over there.
- That's right. Thank you.

14:57.679 --> 14:58.754
