15:57.845 --> 15:58.845
No.

16:01.090 --> 16:05.794
No, I don't want to talk or
think about anything right now.

16:37.378 --> 16:38.458
Jamie?

17:01.511 --> 17:02.627
I'm sorry.

17:05.445 --> 17:06.445
Me too.

17:26.585 --> 17:29.304
Sorry. I'm sorry.

17:29.568 --> 17:31.418
Look, you know I want you,

17:32.118 --> 17:35.964
but I don't want to be this
drug that numbs you out.

17:36.131 --> 17:38.223
Someone that you just
want to get lost in.

17:39.219 --> 17:41.690
Look, when, and if this
is real, let me know.

17:41.692 --> 17:44.071
But please don't use me
because you don't want to deal

17:44.096 --> 17:46.196
